Package math.core.interfaces

package math.core.interfaces
Provides core interfaces for mathematical operations.

Key Features:

  • Type-safe operation contracts for custom number types
  • Extensible design for arithmetic implementations
  • Consistent operation signatures across implementations

Core Interfaces:

  1. Basic arithmetic operations (add, subtract, multiply, divide) provided by (Operable)
  2. Enhanced mathematical operations (inverse, unity) provided by (EnhancedOperable)
Since:
v0.0.15
